.head 4 -  Description: 
.head 4 +  Returns 
.head 5 -  Boolean: 
.head 4 -  Parameters 
.head 4 -  Static Variables 
.head 4 +  Local variables 
.head 5 -  Number: nStatus
.head 4 +  Actions 
